{"word":"διασχίζω","slug":"διασχίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>διασχίζω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>σω</el>) </el><p/><i>to cleave</i> or <i>rend asunder</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be cloven asunder</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; of soldiers, <i>to be separated</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/>"}]}